  <metadata>
    <name>Tour 17: Fleckenstein &amp; Northern Vosges</name>
    <desc>Cross into France to discover the Château du Fleckenstein—a medieval fortress carved into a 30-meter sandstone cliff—and ride the forested roads of the northern Vosges, a UNESCO Biosphere Reserve.</desc>
    <author>
      <name>Hockenheim Motorcycle Tours</name>
    </author>
  </metadata>
